813b5931-eb85-4552-8cb0-87abf8ba43b7	Dottie Dating App	Dottie is a cutting-edge dating app designed with the user in mind. With its sleek and intuitive interface, Dottie aims to simplify the online dating experience while ensuring engagement, usability, and accessibility. My approach to this project emphasized creating a clean, modern design with a focus on a seamless user journey. The app's aesthetic incorporates an orange color palette, promoting energy, warmth, and friendliness - key attributes for a dating platform.	https://utfs.io/f/05122a92-4c42-4e80-ba08-c7ed534abd46-6xgg3o.png	https://www.figma.com/proto/2ri9plawy4HvheDD0LjsCQ/Dottie---Dating-App?node-id=1-3&scaling=scale-down&page-id=0%3A1&starting-point-node-id=1%3A3		f	Personal	UI/UX Design	t	[{"id":"d5a6ff82-066b-4b54-b20f-2e29119f1bf2","type":"paragraph","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[],"children":[]},{"id":"2cb132ab-edea-4e30-8273-d26bd436113b","type":"heading","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Design Philosophy","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"9eaacd42-8c0d-45ac-a4a5-caacd691802f","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Clean, Minimalist Design:\\n","styles":{"bold":true}},{"type":"text","text":"The design approach was centered around simplicity and clarity, ensuring that users can easily navigate and understand the platform. I avoided unnecessary clutter to allow users to focus on the core features‚Äîcreating meaningful connections.","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"09becdd7-7e16-4b3d-887a-a369265fe402","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"User-Centric Approach:\\n","styles":{"bold":true}},{"type":"text","text":"Every design decision was made with the end-user in mind. This means a focus on ease of use, intuitive navigation, and a visually appealing yet functional layout. The goal was to create a dating app that feels inviting, safe, and straightforward.","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"e0e4fac6-a5e2-42a2-b39b-7b7d136c26cc","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Color Palette:","styles":{"bold":true}}],"children":[{"id":"82e0ffa7-6a1c-4246-a199-bc0f82d3a2fb","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Primary Color: Orange\\n","styles":{"bold":true}},{"type":"text","text":"Orange was chosen to evoke feelings of energy, enthusiasm, and warmth‚Äîimportant qualities for a dating app where users are looking to make personal connections. This vibrant color stands out but is balanced with other neutral tones to avoid overwhelming the user.","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"ec28e34b-fad0-4ad8-b5c8-431ddef980b0","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Secondary Colors:","styles":{"bold":true}}],"children":[{"id":"64109909-9e72-44b4-a308-ee3844388efe","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Soft Greys & Whites","styles":{"bold":true}},{"type":"text","text":": Used to maintain clarity and readability while offering a calm contrast to the orange tones. These neutral colors help ensure that the app doesn‚Äôt feel too loud, while keeping the focus on the essential interactive elements.","styles":{}}],"children":[]}]}]},{"id":"f7db3b56-3084-4b63-9186-244e921ee93d","type":"paragraph","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[],"children":[]},{"id":"26575c05-7484-448a-b8da-976e21d89fe5","type":"heading","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Design Process","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"4e6c6930-2e27-43db-83f1-3a0079c4960e","type":"numberedListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Research & Ideation:","styles":{"bold":true}}],"children":[{"id":"9322f98d-d778-49bf-bcf7-16a9cf441518","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"User Research:","styles":{"bold":true}},{"type":"text","text":" Conducted surveys and user interviews to understand the pain points of dating app users. This included analyzing existing competitors to identify areas for improvement in terms of design and user experience.","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"949f7529-f5c9-4b3d-8e5d-fd863e5d31cb","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Persona Creation:","styles":{"bold":true}},{"type":"text","text":" Developed personas based on real user data to ensure the app's design catered to the target demographic, focusing on ease of use, accessibility, and creating emotional connections.","styles":{}}],"children":[]}]},{"id":"66f6e139-60b4-433c-b669-8adc57a5f426","type":"numberedListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Wireframing & Prototyping:","styles":{"bold":true}}],"children":[{"id":"feb5c52c-c3d9-4a7c-9b1f-1021f868e7b5","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Low-Fidelity Wireframes:","styles":{"bold":true}},{"type":"text","text":" Created wireframes to lay out the app‚Äôs key functionalities and structure. This included screens for profile creation, swiping, messaging, and settings.","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"a2a080fb-9958-44bd-8cc6-aeafa4479709","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"High-Fidelity Prototypes:","styles":{"bold":true}},{"type":"text","text":" Once the wireframes were validated, I created high-fidelity prototypes in Figma, incorporating the color palette, typography, and branding. Interactive prototypes allowed for testing user flows and interactions.","styles":{}}],"children":[]}]},{"id":"1797315a-fca6-445a-a6fd-3115c273892f","type":"numberedListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Usability Testing:","styles":{"bold":true}}],"children":[{"id":"f6666632-18c5-44f7-acf5-d05af7fdcf30","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conducted usability tests with a sample group to gather feedback on navigation, ease of interaction, and overall satisfaction with the app's aesthetic and functionality.","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"0102ba12-ad91-43ad-839d-68daa8035445","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Iterated the design based on real-user feedback, refining the app's flow, buttons, and interactions.","styles":{}}],"children":[]}]},{"id":"2b32b3db-4e42-4b38-b850-8e10ba528b39","type":"paragraph","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[],"children":[]},{"id":"737af02d-ea91-4832-ae88-df31884b54ff","type":"heading","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key Features & Design Elements","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"d66f886d-c11e-46c2-bb3a-8ba90a00c013","type":"numberedListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Onboarding Process:","styles":{"bold":true}}],"children":[{"id":"b1fb93d0-2ac8-4c63-acb2-03b30fe00d20","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"The onboarding process was designed to be as seamless as possible, with a simple yet engaging introduction to the app. This included a smooth sign-up process and intuitive user guidance to help new users understand the app's functionalities quickly.","styles":{}}],"children":[]}]},{"id":"b9fb2ddf-1a25-42b5-9df9-8adf583465be","type":"numberedListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Profile Creation & Customization:","styles":{"bold":true}}],"children":[{"id":"47852014-ad07-4c0f-90ae-e23b8eba2133","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Clear, easy-to-follow steps for profile creation, including the ability to upload photos, provide personal information, and select preferences. The profile page itself was designed to be visually appealing, with a modern card-style layout that prioritized user photos.","styles":{}}],"children":[]}]},{"id":"c23bfcec-f683-4518-bc29-1d39ed31ddd6","type":"numberedListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Matching & Swiping Interface:","styles":{"bold":true}}],"children":[{"id":"1d3414a7-ba5a-43db-aa37-ce1e0cf78849","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"The app's matching interface uses large, bold images to keep the user engaged. The swipe feature is intuitive, with an emphasis on simplicity. Swiping was designed with easy-to-tap, clear icons, and quick gestures that fit seamlessly into a mobile interface.","styles":{}}],"children":[]}]},{"id":"3f9e6fb7-230e-4bf6-82ff-818b54b77ec4","type":"numberedListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Messaging System:","styles":{"bold":true}}],"children":[{"id":"766a38ad-9c80-4fd5-8d42-a474f8595b6b","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Messaging is central to the app‚Äôs core functionality. The chat interface was designed to feel casual yet polished, allowing users to quickly communicate with each other without distractions. Message bubbles are color-coded with soft grays and whites, maintaining the clean look of the app.","styles":{}}],"children":[]}]},{"id":"b56f9bb2-43e0-49ca-845b-a5092023a60b","type":"numberedListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Navigation:","styles":{"bold":true}}],"children":[{"id":"7aa6b399-a771-4ec3-b88a-c5081f3573fe","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"The bottom navigation bar was designed with a minimalist approach, incorporating clear icons for Home, Search, Messages, and Profile. The goal was to make navigation intuitive and reduce cognitive load, allowing users to access key features without feeling overwhelmed.","styles":{}}],"children":[]}]},{"id":"93de08b2-7019-4cb3-99e5-d452b79d6906","type":"paragraph","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[],"children":[]},{"id":"2bee7edc-c59b-434e-af9c-2857338b9c33","type":"heading","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Typography","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"935c7d24-280d-4687-95ea-67a56726528f","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Primary Typeface:","styles":{"bold":true}}],"children":[{"id":"a9a16f43-09ce-4d30-986f-2cefd28fd991","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"A modern sans-serif font was chosen for readability and a clean, polished aesthetic. This font reflects the app's contemporary and approachable tone, while maintaining legibility on both mobile and desktop views.","styles":{}}],"children":[]}]},{"id":"d22f9787-98c5-4392-9ef5-41566b0b8062","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Secondary Typeface:","styles":{"bold":true}}],"children":[{"id":"e1e9d5c1-0d2e-4b32-a5be-93830e926541","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"A slightly more playful, yet still simple, secondary font was used for call-to-action buttons and headings to create a friendly and engaging atmosphere.","styles":{}}],"children":[]}]},{"id":"155dc7f1-27b3-406b-bbd8-14be7eada0fa","type":"paragraph","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[],"children":[]},{"id":"5dd88633-3635-4ea9-8e83-1252f7def606","type":"heading","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Accessibility Considerations","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"a34f84ea-d1f2-46e0-b6c0-9c5399797516","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default","textAlignment":"left"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Color Contrast:\\n","styles":{"bo